### 查询课程信息
POST {{gateway_host}}/content/course/list?pageNo=1&pageSize=2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "auditStatus": "202004",
  "courseName": "java",
  "publishStatus": "203001"
}

<> 2026-01-25T191324.200.json


### 查询课程分类
GET {{content_host}}/content/course-category/tree-nodes


### 创建课程
